### **SEO Mistakes**

<div class="my-6 p-6 bg-red-50 border-l-4 border-red-500">

#### **Mistake #13: Ignoring SEO Basics**

**THE PROBLEM:** 78% of AI-built sites lack basic SEO.

**CONSEQUENCE:**
- Invisible in Google search
- Zero organic traffic
- Wasted potential
- Dependence on paid ads

**THE FIX:**
- Optimize page titles (include keywords)
- Add meta descriptions
- Use header tags (H1, H2, H3)
- Optimize images (alt text, file names)
- Create sitemap
- Submit to Google Search Console

</div>

---

<div class="my-6 p-6 bg-orange-50 border-l-4 border-orange-500">

#### **Mistake #14: Duplicate Content**

**THE PROBLEM:** AI generates similar content across sites.

**CONSEQUENCE:**
- Google penalizes duplicate content
- Poor rankings
- Won't index properly
- Wasted effort

**THE FIX:**
- Write original content
- Use AI for ideas, not final copy
- Check for plagiarism
- Add unique perspective
- Personalize with your voice

</div>

