<div class="my-6 p-6 bg-amber-50 border-l-4 border-amber-500">

#### **Mistake #15: No Local SEO (For Local Businesses)**

**THE PROBLEM:** Local businesses don't optimize for local search.

**CONSEQUENCE:**
- Invisible in "near me" searches
- Losing to competitors with better local SEO
- Zero local organic traffic

**THE FIX:**
- Create Google Business Profile
- Get reviews (4.5+ stars)
- Add location pages
- Include address and phone
- Use local keywords

</div>

