### **E-Commerce Mistakes**

<div class="my-6 p-6 bg-red-50 border-l-4 border-red-500">

#### **Mistake #16: Poor Product Photos**

**THE PROBLEM:** Low-quality or few product images.

**CONSEQUENCE:**
- Low conversion (1-2% vs 3-5%)
- Returns (product doesn't match expectations)
- Low trust
- Fewer sales

**THE FIX:**
- Multiple angles per product
- High-resolution images
- Lifestyle photos (products in use)
- Zoom functionality
- Video demonstrations

</div>

---

<div class="my-6 p-6 bg-orange-50 border-l-4 border-orange-500">

#### **Mistake #17: Hidden Shipping Costs**

**THE PROBLEM:** Shipping revealed at checkout (cart abandonment).

**CONSEQUENCE:**
- 68% cart abandonment rate
- Surprise at checkout
- Lost sales
- Negative experience

**THE FIX:**
- Show shipping upfront
- Offer free shipping threshold
- Be transparent about costs
- Calculate shipping in cart (not checkout)
- Consider shipping-included pricing

</div>

---

<div class="my-6 p-6 bg-amber-50 border-l-4 border-amber-500">

#### **Mistake #18: Complicated Checkout**

**THE PROBLEM:** Too many steps, required account creation.

**CONSEQUENCE:**
- High cart abandonment
- Frustrated customers
- Lost sales at final step

**THE FIX:**
- Guest checkout option
- Minimal form fields
- Progress indicator
- Multiple payment options
- One-page checkout when possible

</div>

