### **Strategic Mistakes**

<div class="my-6 p-6 bg-red-50 border-l-4 border-red-500">

#### **Mistake #19: No Email Capture**

**THE PROBLEM:** 71% of sites don't capture visitor emails.

**CONSEQUENCE:**
- One-time visitors only
- Can't remarket
- Lost future revenue
- No customer relationship

**THE FIX:**
- Add email capture above fold
- Offer lead magnet (guide, discount)
- Use popup (timed appropriately)
- Create email newsletter
- Build email list from day 1

</div>

