**THE PROBLEM:** No social proof from early customers.

**CONSEQUENCE:**
- Lower trust
- Harder to convert new customers
- Missing powerful marketing asset

**THE FIX:**
- Ask every customer for feedback
- Make it easy (one-click request)
- Offer incentive for testimonials
- Display prominently
- Use in marketing

</div>

