**THE PROBLEM:** Spending weeks/months perfecting before launch.

**CONSEQUENCE:**
- Lost time
- No real-world feedback
- Missed opportunities
- Analysis paralysis

**THE FIX:**
- Launch "good enough" version
- Get real user feedback
- Iterate based on data
- Improve over time
- Speed beats perfection

